data.description: ***PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!!*** Looking for a wonderful home with the harmony of space and comfort? Your search ends here with this lovely home located in Northeast Columbia! This three-bedroom home features a versatile upstairs loft, which can be used as a home office, entertainment space, play room, media room, the choices are endless. The serene balcony offers an ideal retreat as you partake on a morning cup of coffee, or to relax after a long day. The floorplan is functional with a large living room, open kitchen and formal dining room, that may be used as a bonus room. The backyard is large enough for everyone to enjoy, including the adorable pets. This home is close to shopping, parks, interstates and only 15-20 minutes from Fort Jackson and Downtown Columbia. It's very convenient to many amenities!
